        "filename": "ner_conc_en_2024-04-07T07.00.22E1712473222.647069.json",
        "en_title": "Regional, for Piedmont the M5s chooses Sarah Disabato",
        "en_content": "For the Presidency of the\nPiedmont Region the 5 Stars Movement Sarah Disabato.\n\n\nThe president of the council group pentastellato in Palazzo\nLascaris and regional coordinator M5s was chosen as\ncandidate to challenge the opponents of centerright and\ncentrosinistra, Alberto Cirio and Gianna Pentenero.\n\n\nThe formalization of the application arrived during a\nPress conference to which the Vice-President is present\nM5s, the former mayor of Turin Chiara Appendino.\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
